Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,————————————————————- ＯＰ————————————————————\N-
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.35,0:01:28.68,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果てしない空をゆく
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.78,0:01:32.07,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,見えない翼が導く
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.18,0:01:34.09,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遥か彼方
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.19,0:01:40.83,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,300)}僕らを待つ　まだ見ぬ未来へと
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.43,0:01:50.49,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Always　覚め切ってた
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.66,0:01:53.49,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,速すぎるthat night
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.69,0:02:00.23,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,透明な闇に囲まれ　誰も似た輪の中で
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.33,0:02:03.30,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Find you　あの日の風
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.42,0:02:06.63,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,揺れ動いた場所
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.71,0:02:07.96,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Eternal my pass
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.01,0:02:12.91,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全て君に合うためのプロセスだったね
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.30,0:02:16.00,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Slowly opened my eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.06,0:02:18.43,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We need the brightness
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.91,0:02:22.37,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彼方から聞こえる予感に
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.42,0:02:26.47,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鼓動を震わせていたいから
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.89,0:02:30.26,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's a reality　It's a reality
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.32,0:02:33.74,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you can believe myself for again
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.85,0:02:37.14,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光の中 目覚めていく
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.19,0:02:40.80,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信じてくれた君となら
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.86,0:02:42.00,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Never let it go
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.05,0:02:43.24,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Never lost my way
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.28,0:02:46.62,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ここで生まれ変わる景色
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.75,0:02:50.20,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傷さえ今　誇りになる
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.24,0:02:54.81,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)}だから君とBurst The Gravity
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.01,0:00:11.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.35,0:01:28.68,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在沒有盡頭的天空中行走
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.78,0:01:32.07,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由看不見的羽翼引導
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.18,0:01:34.09,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通向遙遠的比方
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.19,0:01:40.83,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,300)}那看不見的未來依舊在等待我們
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.43,0:01:50.49,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Always 不願清醒
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.66,0:01:53.49,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太快了 that night
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.69,0:02:00.23,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被那透明的黑暗包圍 誰也逃不出這個圈
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.33,0:02:03.30,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Find you 那日的風
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.42,0:02:06.63,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,變幻不定的場所
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.71,0:02:07.96,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Eternal my pass
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.01,0:02:12.91,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這一切都是為了與你相會
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.30,0:02:16.00,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Slowly opened my eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.06,0:02:18.43,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We need the brightness
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.91,0:02:22.37,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自彼方聽聞的預感
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.42,0:02:26.47,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,令我震動鼓舞
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.89,0:02:30.26,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's a reality　It's a reality
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.32,0:02:33.74,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you can believe myself for again
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.85,0:02:37.14,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在光的沐浴下 我漸漸清醒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.19,0:02:40.80,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若是你 我相信
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.86,0:02:42.00,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Never let it go
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.05,0:02:43.24,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Never lost my way
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.28,0:02:46.62,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這裏不斷變化的景色
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.75,0:02:50.20,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在的傷口 是我的驕傲
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.24,0:02:54.81,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)}因為你和Burst The Gravity
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,————————————————————- ＯＰ————————————————————\N-
